Catalogue of a Genuine Collection of Paintings, including An Unique Cabinet of Miniature Pictures in oil...removed from Brussels within this Month, the entire Property of Mr. M. van PARYS. Which, by order of the Executors, will be sold by Auction by Mr. Phillips (London), June 4 & 5, 1832; 2nd Day, June 5: Lot 203 In one Lot...An Unique and Portable Cabinet of 315 Minature Gems...as hereunder described: (The number refers to the panel in which is contained one or more Pictures. Large Drawer, N° 2: 147 Breughel - The Tower of Babel [Lugt, Répert. 13007]; [toegevoegde vermelding]: cf. picture coll. G. van Berg & Clovio; V&A L. (Picture Catal. XIV - (23.PP)).
